    rdfs:comment """Section containing information about a FENE potential: $V(r) = -\\frac{1}{2} k R_0^2 \\ln \\left[ 1 - \\left( \\frac{r - r_0}{R_0} \\right)^2 \\right] + C$,
$k$ is the `force_constant`, $r_0$ is the `equilibrium_value` of $r$, and $R_0$ is the
maximum allowable bond extension beyond $r_0$. $C$ is an arbitrary constant (not stored).""" ;
    rdfs:subClassOf <https://fairmat-nfdi.github.io/nomad-simulations/rdf/section/nomad.datamodel.data.ArchiveSection>,
